The repository contains all your Chrome extension files with the recent changes where I removed the two settings options:
- ❌ "Auto-calculate on page load" (now always enabled)
- ❌ "Show calculation breakdown" (now always enabled)

The extension now has a cleaner, simpler settings interface with just the Daily Budget and Tikkie Link options.
